parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shut-off of the engine can cause loss of power steering and braking, increasing the risk of accidents, especially on high-speed roads.
symptoms: The engine shuts off without warning
no warning messages or symptoms before the shut-off
loss of power steering and braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the backup camera can increase the risk of accidents, especially when reversing, as the driver may not be able to see obstacles or pedestrians behind the vehicle.
symptoms: The backup camera display becomes grainy
the backup camera display goes black
the camera system flashes on and off
the camera system displays a partial picture.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the blind spot monitoring system can increase the risk of accidents, especially when changing lanes or merging with traffic, as the driver may not be aware of vehicles in the blind spot.
symptoms: The driver side blind spot monitor fails to detect vehicles
the system fails to alert the driver of vehicles in the blind spot
the system may randomly work and then fail again.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission shift control can cause the vehicle to move unexpectedly, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle fails to engage into park
the vehicle drifts or moves forward after shutting down
the vehicle does not respond to the engine/start button
the vehicle moves without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission bearings can cause the transmission to slip, leading to loss of control, accidents, and damage to other vehicle components.
symptoms: Noise in the front driver side
the vehicle feels like it's pulling or sputtering
the transmission slips
loss of control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seatbelt locking mechanism can compromise the safety of passengers, especially in the event of an accident, and may lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The seatbelt lock is missing
the seatbelt buckle does not latch
the receiver piece for the buckle gets jammed
the seatbelt does not buckle properly.
